    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are explicitly scoped out per the MRL 2 assessment plan, consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB use context described in the bound requirement (https://uofa.net/morrison/req/cpb-hemolysis-mrl2) and claim (https://uofa.net/morrison/claim/cpb-hemolysis-worst-case). Decision: Accepted at Medium assurance level.",
